1. Kubernetes: Run

2. Terminal: kubectl proxy => browse to http://localhost:8001/ui

3. Kubernetes: Load => deployments/express-docker

4. JSON: Remove ResourceVersion

5. JSON: Change replicas: 3

6. Terminal: kubectl apply -f deployments-express-docker.json

7. Browse to http://localhost:8001/ui

8. Terminal: kubectl expose deployments/express-docker --port=80 --target-port=3000 --type=LoadBalancer

9. kubectl get svc -w => wait for <external-ip>

10. Browse to <external-ip>
